Package: cie11cl
Title: ICD-11 (CIE-11) Access and ICD-10 to ICD-11 Crosswalks for Chile
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Rodolfo", "Tasso", , "rtasso@uchile.cl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Deterministic access to the World Health Organization
    International Classification of Diseases, 11th Revision (ICD-11, MMS
    linearization) in Spanish, with code lookup, lexical search and
    ICD-10 to ICD-11 crosswalks carrying traceable certainty levels,
    oriented to the Chilean health system. The package ships code only:
    users load their own ICD-11 release and mapping tables at runtime; no
    classification data is bundled. The same input plus the same versioned
    reference data always yields the same output.
